    "created_at": "2014-10-21T22:53:02Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-10-21T22:53:49Z",
    "body": "I don't think we should _explain_ why the standard library is poorly designed. The problem should be fixed by not making confusing mazes of re-exports. Crates should just be used directly and the prelude could include those crates and `use` directly from them instead of the current mess.\n",
